data.title: Frank Scully - Behind The Flying Saucers
data.meta_description: Frank Scully - Behind the Flying Saucers - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Vintage book about UFO'S- From cover: At last, readers have the full-length fascinating inside story of those disks which have caused so much excitement. Here are the theories and actualities of magnetic propulsion, eyewitness accounts of disks discovered in the magnetic fault zones of the west --disks made of material unknown on this earth, diskx carrying such extraordinary devices and machines as to confound our most brilliant experts.
